<ul>
<li><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/furikake/">Plugin</a></li>
<li><a href="http://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/601.html">CWE Definition of Open Redirects</a></li>
<li><a href="https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2017-1000434">CVE-2017-1000434</a></li>
</ul>
